      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people care but it doesnt change the fact that i failed. everyone expects so much from me and i just cant meet it anymore. it feels like there's no point in even trying to fix things when the damage is already done. it's just this constant, heavy exhaustion. it's like being stuck in a loop where every exit is blocked. do you ever feel like some things are just fundamentally broken beyond repair?",
